{"title":"新城","authors":["钟永华"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":2,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"新城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钟永华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一重重峻峭的山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一幅幅奇丽的画，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽情地升腾，舒展，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各怀夙愿，各怀憧憬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以各自独有的线条，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勾勒出一个童话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塑造出一座新城。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓬勃兴起的大厦群呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何不沿着往常的轨迹上升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却伸出透明的椭圆形的双翼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩蝶般翩跹着美妙的圆舞曲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"系着翻飞的思绪亲吻阳春？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，你不满足于高耸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却向往大海壮阔无垠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新月般光洁的楼台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蘑菇般活脱的塔顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玲珑别致的扇形高阁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"富丽华美的星座旋厅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摒弃一切陈旧的结构，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦一般地追求，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突破，焕发着灿烂和清新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大胆地摒弃、追求，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大胆走向竞逐和延伸。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}